					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"There's nowhere I can't go with Misaki beside me — to the ends of the earth, through fire, wind, water, and even heart.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"只要和美岬在一起——地球内侧也好，围墙内也好，天堂也好，地狱也好，高潮也好——我哪都去得了。",
